cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.DS 

The paper discusses the issue of sensitive data leakage in machine learning models, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also proposes practical algorithms for "memorizing" information about the training dataset, which is a core topic in machine learning (cs.LG). The specific tasks evaluated in the paper, such as image classification and face recognition, are also commonly studied in the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. Additionally, the use of ML frameworks and services for non-experts suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and the practical implementation of these algorithms may involve data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
